data.description: This beautiful 4- bedroom, 2-bath home is located in a charming neighborhood in Texhoma. It offers plenty of space with a spacious living area, perfect for family gatherings and entertaining friends and family. The beds provide a cozy retreat. The backyard is a true gem, offering a peaceful oasis to relax and enjoy.
